Example outputs of the functions within the package

ec_output_demo.Rd

List of different economic complexity computations obtained by using the functions within the package. The output is provided as a list of data frames.

ec_output_demo

Format

A list of data frames with 3 elements.

rca

`rca()` output (single data frame)

complexity

`complexity()` output (list of four data frames)

value

`proximity()` output (list of two data frames)

Examples
